{
  "stem": "27409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And luckily, I had the-- my letters from my guards from this [INAUDIBLE] front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The girls, and soldiers, the clerks-- all they're armed of course, and they knew how to use a weapon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we moved on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's were dangerous territory because of the remnants of the German army still there in the forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were Poles and Ukrainians which fought on the side of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then they are attacking us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not know about the camps, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't have with whom to speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] This from witness as a Jew-- I don't remember just in the moment the name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told me his family has-- was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was in the army, and the family was killed by Germans that he knew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They capitulate, so I did not go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I ask-- they asked me-- first, I formally-- on the way, I popped over to see my parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because in going to Japan, I say when will I return, if I return-- if I am alive?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I made myself an order out, took another officer with me, and we went.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had luggage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was for Czechoslovakia, on the way, Czechoslovakia, Poland to Krakow there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I took-- I bought in Moravska Ostrava-- tell you the town-- I bought needle, I bought things of-- which you can use in barter.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I took it with my colleague to schlep and to there on the roof.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We went on the train, the roof, so [INAUDIBLE] to Cernauti there, my uncle, which was not deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from there we went with a truck to-- just jumped on a truck and went to Strozhnitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you can imagine, suddenly then I appeared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my own name.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
